                            <comment id="39050" author="laisiyao" created="Fri, 18 May 2012 04:08:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sarah, what failure did you get? The console log reported several soft lockup (on different &apos;ls&apos; processes), but this may be reasonable because lock contention can be heavy in racer test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
